Title: An Act Changing the Name of the De La Paz Elementary School in the Municipality of Banate, Province of Iloilo, to Jose J. Bacaling Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 815
An Act Changing the Name of the De La Paz Elementary School in the Municipality of Banate, Province of Iloilo, to Jose J. Bacaling Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the De La Paz Elementary School in the Municipality of Banate, Province of Iloilo, is changed to Jose J. Bacaling Elementary School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.1a\^/phi1
Approved: April 27, 1984
